# Cloudflare Pages handles .html → clean-URL automatically via "Pretty URLs".
# These serve the files without triggering HTTP redirects (status 200 = rewrite).
# Do NOT use 301/302 here — that causes ERR_TOO_MANY_REDIRECTS when combined
# with Pages' built-in pretty-URL redirect for /page.html → /page.
/              /index.html    200
/privacy       /privacy.html  200
/terms         /terms.html    200
/dmca          /dmca.html     200
/support       /support.html  200
